00:15:00.330 --> 00:15:02.330
ar fi reprezentate prin puncte ca acestea.

00:15:02.330 --> 00:15:05.330
Am ridica de la 3% din terenurile arabile, 4%.

00:15:05.330 --> 00:15:09.330
